** About you **   
If you have a passion for optimising IT systems and providing efficient,
quality service for our team to thrive, we invite you to join our team and
contribute to our mission of delivering for the Australian sugarcane industry.  
  
** To Apply **   
You must have the right to live and work in Australia to be considered for
this role.  
  
The successful applicant will be required to undertake pre-employment
screening which includes an online medical screening and police check.

